OL,11,Fdoor of his home after he pressed an   
OL,12,Femergency call button around his neck. 
OL,14,FWhen she got there she discovered the  
OL,15,F89-year-old Suez Crisis veteran also   
OL,16,Fhad a broken shoulder.                 
OL,18,FThe Welsh Ambulance Service said Mr    
OL,19,FRyan's experience was below the service
OL,20,Fit aimed to offer.                     
